DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-1.384ft at 06:54\n-2.964ft at 08:30\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Modest scale mix of WNW swell and SSW swell for thigh-waist high surf. Fav
 orable early morning tide push\, then later AM/mid day higher tide slows t
 ide sensitive breaks. Incoming tide helps again later afternoon/evening. \
 n\nLight S winds much of the morning\, shifting SW and puffing up to low-e
 nd moderate over the afternoon for some lump. 
END:VEVENT
