BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260403T065400
DTEND:20260403T103000
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.102ft at 06:54\n-2.947ft at 10:30\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Nice blend of NW swell and longer-period SSW/S swell looks good for waist 
 to shoulder high surf in the morning\, tapering off a bit over the afterno
 on. Incoming tide push helps much of the morning\, then the higher mid day
  tide bogs down tide sensitive spots some. \n\nLight\, primarily offshore 
 winds expected through the day. 
END:VEVENT
