DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.002ft at 07:24\n-2.95ft at 11:36\n\nOBSERVATION:\nA
  fair size blend of steeper-angled\, selective SSW/S swell rolls in\, as s
 horter-period NW swell fades. Good southerly exposures are waist to chest 
 high\, while focal points see head high sets on the morning tide push. \n\
 nLight winds due all day\, offshore most of the morning\, SW sea breeze in
  the afternoon. 
